<SecondaryPreamble>
<IntroductoryText>
<P>
<Text>In accordance with section 4 of the Scottish Civil Justice Council and Criminal Legal Assistance Act 2013<FootnoteRef Ref="f00001"/>, the Court of Session has approved draft rules submitted to it by the Scottish Civil Justice Council with such modifications as it thinks appropriate.</Text></P>
</IntroductoryText>
<EnactingText>
<Para>
<Text>The Court of Session therefore makes this Act of Sederunt under the powers conferred by sections 103(1) and 104(1) of the Courts Reform (Scotland) Act 2014<FootnoteRef Ref="f00002"/> and all other powers enabling it to do so.</Text></Para>
</EnactingText>
